{"tid":1871600,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[借ac] 【衛生防護中心提供家居檢疫大廈名單疑有錯漏】","createTime":"2020-02-09T14:26:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-09T14:59:04.000Z","uid":284044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"00db25fd6d7d6e8fe1c31571b944d5596f38545a","tid":1871600,"uid":284044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T14:26:31.000Z","msg":"唔係想借呢到宣傳，但我認為呢個資訊真係要畀多啲人知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記者整合家居檢疫大廈名單時，發現衛生防護中心公布的名單中，在九龍城區及觀塘區各新增了2座大廈，這4座大廈完成檢疫日期介乎2月8日至13日，但記者翻查2月4日的名單，未見這4座大廈。換言之，若這些大廈是需要進行14家居檢疫，在2月4日的名單中或有錯漏。未知這些大廈需檢疫日數較短，或是有其他原因。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JSnJzB9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJSnJzB9.png&h=71e442e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2月4日名單整合圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/up5Gmhm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fup5Gmhm.png&h=07ae4904&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2p1Y7Xm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2p1Y7Xm.png&h=5c5b16d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n衛生防護中心公布pdf原圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TuVveCx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTuVveCx.png&h=dbea2a58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/78EgaaS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F78EgaaS.png&h=c4f92127&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ssWm5Kd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FssWm5Kd.png&h=ec0c2849&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y6Rycpd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy6Rycpd.png&h=007bb833&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原PO<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/firsthandnewshk/posts/181364589880207\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffirs